--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Project description:
This is a system is designed to help students manage their academic tasks, track their study habits, and improve productivity in a simple 
and effective way. It integrates task management, mood tracking, and study time analysis into one platform to support better study planning.

